message.body: Hey! I hope you are good! Looks like you got a bunch going on - but if you want to meet at the studio next Saturday for a couple of hours that would be amazing!
I'm so sorry I didn't get back to you sooner! Was in VA and working so much! I can do a few hours next Saturday. We head to New Jersey in the afternoon. Wanna say 10:30???
It's no problem - can't wait to hear about everything!! Sounds exciting. - yes - 10:30 is perfect!
Awesome! Hope you have a good week!
